.: Full markdown hygiene pass on a .md file — lint fixes, MD rule scan, semantic advisory analysis. Triggers — lint markdown, fix markdown, MD violations, markdownlint pass, hygiene check, markdown hygiene, markdown hygiene skill, markdown hygiene workflow
markdown-hygiene-analysis: Semantic advisory scan of a .md file against SA001-SA038 rules. Triggers — analysis phase, SA rules, semantic advisory, style advisories, markdown hygiene analysis, markdown hygiene analysis skill, markdown hygiene analysis workflow
markdown-hygiene-lint: MD rule violation scan for a .md file. Fixes known safe rules in-place before scanning. Triggers — lint phase, MD violations, markdownlint scan, markdown hygiene lint, markdown hygiene lint skill, markdown hygiene lint workflow
markdown-hygiene-result: Check cache state of a markdown-hygiene sub-document. Returns path and cache status for report, lint, or analysis, markdown hygiene result, markdown hygiene result skill, markdown hygiene result workflow
